  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/7e8aa7e5b92ad8aa37562880c93b9294.avif?t=1770844835\" width=620 height=140 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"The clinking of chains...\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They said you were sick. Prescribed pills. Begged you to stay in touch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But you chose solitude — just you, your cat, and the old house.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/68868ec4cb8ee1d8fa104a1cc1633f65.poster.avif?t=1770844835\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/68868ec4cb8ee1d8fa104a1cc1633f65.webm?t=1770844835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/68868ec4cb8ee1d8fa104a1cc1633f65.mp4?t=1770844835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"The clinking of chains...\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up, as always, to feed your cat. But something is off: one of the doors is locked, and the key is nowhere to be found. A metallic ringing echoes in your head. In the bathroom, something rotten flickers into sight—then vanishes. And on the mirror... a note from your childhood doll.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Memories stir. Your grandmother’s curse — forgotten, but never gone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/b9190fde232fbc04d403fd1de0544b5f.poster.avif?t=1770844835\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/b9190fde232fbc04d403fd1de0544b5f.webm?t=1770844835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/b9190fde232fbc04d403fd1de0544b5f.mp4?t=1770844835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"The clinking of chains...\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why did she do this to you?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"The clinking of chains...\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you explore the house, you piece the doll back together — and suddenly, a hidden passage appears in the garage. It leads to a world from your dreams. Or your past. Or your madness. Endless stairways, coffins in the walls, worm-infested tunnels. They call to you — and terrify you all the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/c2d17593f991ed5fc8b8cbce3c668fa2.poster.avif?t=1770844835\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/c2d17593f991ed5fc8b8cbce3c668fa2.webm?t=1770844835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/c2d17593f991ed5fc8b8cbce3c668fa2.mp4?t=1770844835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"The clinking of chains...\"</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What is that damned sound echoing in your mind?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/b60702d8d549733601290abbc31e57d3.poster.avif?t=1770844835\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/b60702d8d549733601290abbc31e57d3.webm?t=1770844835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/b60702d8d549733601290abbc31e57d3.mp4?t=1770844835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/9f549c5f1e169780da5575c89c504988.avif?t=1770844835\" width=620 height=140 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. A classic walking simulator with a psychological horror twist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Explore your home and uncover hidden objects to unlock the story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. Solve light puzzles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/69aee02abb05932fd06ee90b247afb48.poster.avif?t=1770844835\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/69aee02abb05932fd06ee90b247afb48.webm?t=1770844835\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/69aee02abb05932fd06ee90b247afb48.mp4?t=1770844835\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/41b784a0955f612269c7d3d3d5e4099d.avif?t=1770844835\" width=620 height=140 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. The game has autosave.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Realistic graphics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. High-quality sound design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Average game completion time: 60 minutes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5. Genre: Walking Simulator.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3494130/extras/c13eac2ce776d345e4e92b1d6ecca51a.avif?t=1770844835\" width=620 height=140 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Note! The game features machine translation into the following languages:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- French</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- German</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Spanish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Portuguese (Brazilian)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Chinese (Simplified)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Korean</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Polish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Japanese</p>",
